        <a href="/blog/online-base64-to-file/" class="block rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-4 no-underline hover:shadow-level-3 transition-all"><p class="text-[14px] font-medium leading-5 text-ink">Base64 to Downloadable File</p><p class="text-[12px] leading-4 text-mute mt-1">Turn encoded strings back into real files</p></a>
        <a href="/blog/bash-base64-decode/" class="block rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-4 no-underline hover:shadow-level-3 transition-all"><p class="text-[14px] font-medium leading-5 text-ink">How to Decode Base64 in Bash</p><p class="text-[12px] leading-4 text-mute mt-1">Linux, WSL, and macOS command line</p></a>
